    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont want to \"make it bearable.\" i don't want to find ways to cope with a life that feels broken. i just want the weight to stop. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to end, but everything just keeps dragging on. it feels like there's no point in even trying to reach the other side of this.",
